Introduction

Anna is a Japanese singer, dancer, model, and actress under The Black Label. She is the sub vocalist of the girl group MEOVV.

On August 27, 2024, Anna was revealed as the fourth member of MEOVV. The group officially debuted on September 6, 2024, with their debut digital single "MEOW".
